channel.title: RuneSpawn - Team Needed
channel.description:
Hello everyone on MoparScape. Im Anthony and im 15. Apparently ive decided to come back to Runescape private servers. I can code servers and setup websites and voting system via the Mysql database and host. Apparently i need 2 coders and a staff team. This project will be based on coding the most unique and best runescape spawn server/PVP. Coder's will get administrator ingame and help me code. They can get paid once i get some decent amount of money. Ill be hosting and everything, ill be also making the website.
THE BASE WILL BE PROJECT-INSANITY.
Im also looking for one Forum Developer to help me with coding forums.
Available Spots:
[code]Forum Developer [1] FULL Server Coder [2] FULL Moderator Ingame [1 for now][/code]
If your interested to apply please post with the following format.
[code]Real Name: Age: Applying for: Experiences: Msn/Skype:[/code]
Thank you, Anthony.
